---
title: Halloumi & Roast Veggie Salad with Indian Coconut Sauce
description: It's roast halloumi, but not as you know it! We're using our mild yet flavourful North Indian spice blend to lift succulent halloumi
to new heights. With a generous helping of roasted veggies, It's all you need to create a meal fit for royalty!

